    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading in the clear coat on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all major electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it does have a minor oil leak and will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a functional driver that simply shows the honest wear of its years on the road.",
