      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood, along with various small dings and scratches from years of use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that isn't perfect but still has plenty of life left.",
