      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail of this automobile reflects an uncompromising commitment to preservation, from its flawless exterior finish to its meticulously kept interior. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade specimen that performs with the precision of a new machine. Discerning buyers will appreciate the unparalleled integrity of this offering.",
